:"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c27039bdc122511dca60c98a6158595851d967","tid":1629001,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"226aa4cc9adbd7520f84005dea66d4417144496d","tid":1629001,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeca9cffd7bb8bf71d4c5201a6bbde35e1daf3f2","tid":1629001,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d857f4d13a314b880c6a32fba4a709672be19783","tid":1629001,"uid":115096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"既然法庭認為《緊急法》有懷疑，《蒙面法》在存疑下產生，其實都可以出禁令。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"見有巴打話因為香港三權分立(其他已死) 所以關係到另一權既要批禁制令門檻係好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"當時梁游案咪即時出禁制令阻止佢地再宣誓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"wiki:<br />\n10月19日的會議中，首項議程是安排黃定光、姚松炎等議員逐一宣誓。姚松炎宣誓後，建制派議員集體離場抗議，並要求點算法定人數，觸發立法會流會，以致梁頌恆、游蕙禎及劉小麗無法再次宣誓<br />\n<br />\n10月26日，梁頌恆和游蕙禎在七名民主派議員及傳媒的「護送」下成功進入會議廳，民主黨並無參與護送<br />\n10月25日，立法會主席梁君彥決定調動議程，決定只安排劉小麗宣誓，押後青年新政議員梁頌恆和游蕙禎再宣誓，亦不容許二人進入會議廳開會。"},{"pid":"41a51f349eb6bc1345c0e71f8d7ae69b6837775a","tid":1629001,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707c15c33720f0e89090002b85c4a9536fb0aa57","tid":1629001,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a55881b15a9de11b808da2b4f968f3a965952d8e","tid":1629001,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c27039bdc122511dca60c98a6158595851d967","tid":1629001,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"226aa4cc9adbd7520f84005dea66d4417144496d","tid":1629001,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeca9cffd7bb8bf71d4c5201a6bbde35e1daf3f2","tid":1629001,"uid":31151,"lik